{
  "stem": "10825.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And he came to the hospital and took us out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And I must tell you, we made so much friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And-- and the whole faculty of the doctors, they loved us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "They gave us a farewell party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they loved us very, very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And we came to Omsk in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "When you-- when you are talking, it freezes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] When-- when you breathe, you can't breathe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "It freezes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And then we came in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And my friend went right away-- you couldn't go into a store and buy something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "But on the-- on the market, like they call the black market, they brought [NON-ENGLISH]-- it means shoes that you can wear in the snow and the frost-- and underwear and one pair of mittens.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "For me, one, and for my husband, one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And the next day, we went, and we took part in the concert.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And my husband sat down to the piano, and Weiner was directing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And-- and he was-- the tears was running down his cheeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Luckily, he was with the back to the audience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "He couldn't imagine that he will play like that with one hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And that is the end of the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "We joined the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This-- this was in-- in '40-- still and '41, and the beginning of '42.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were together then until '44.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came back to-- we was-- we were all over the Soviet Union, even in the-- in the-- in the far east.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came back to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived through a pogrom in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A Jew came back from the war with a lot of medals.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a hero.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got the highest awards that a-- that a military man can.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
